## QUICK START

### 1. Azure Environment Setup (M1)
```bash
# Create resource group
az group create --name thinkfunding-rg --location eastus

# Create App Service Plan
az appservice plan create --name tf-api-plan --resource-group thinkfunding-rg --sku B1

# Create Web App (API)
az webapp create --name thinkfunding-api --resource-group thinkfunding-rg --plan tf-api-plan --runtime "DOTNET|8.0"

# Create SQL Database
az sql server create --name thinkfunding-sql --resource-group thinkfunding-rg --admin-user sqladmin --admin-password <secure>

# Create Blob Storage
az storage account create --name thinkfundingstore --resource-group thinkfunding-rg --sku Standard_LRS
```

### 2. Clone & Setup
```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd ThinkFunding

# Backend
cd src/api
dotnet restore
dotnet build

# Frontend
cd ../web
npm install
npm start
```

### 3. Environment Variables
```bash
# API (.env)
AZURE_SQL_CONNECTION_STRING=
AZURE_BLOB_CONNECTION_STRING=
ENTRA_CLIENT_ID=
ENTRA_CLIENT_SECRET=
ENTRA_TENANT_ID=
JWT_SECRET=

# Web (.env)
REACT_APP_API_URL=
REACT_APP_ENTRA_CLIENT_ID=
```

